THE GAME
--------

  'Oslide' is played on an 11 by 11 tile board with an empty space
in the center. The idea is to move tiles so that 3 tiles of the
same pattern line up, either horizontally or vertically. When 3
tiles with the same pattern are lined up, their patterns are
removed making them empty tiles (but still moveable). The goal is
to clear all the tiles in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

